'''''Red Moon''''' is the second game in the ''[[Time and Magik]]'' trilogy.

==Gameplay==
Red Moon Crystal, a powerful source of Magik, has been stolen and must be recovered to save the country of Baskalos from destruction.<ref name="zzap64">{{ citation | url=https://archive.org/stream/zzap64-magazine-003/ZZap_64_Issue_003_1985_Jul#page/n85/mode/2up | journal=[[Zzap!64]] | publisher=[[Newsfield Publications Ltd]] | title = Level 9's big red moon | date=June 1985 | issue=1 | pages=67–68 }}</ref>

==Reception==
{{Video game reviews
| award1Pub = Crash
| award1 = Smash!<ref>Game review, Crash issue 20, September 1985, page 91</ref>
